CodeWars Checkpoint – 300 Points Challenge
Overview

This checkpoint is designed to track your progress in solving algorithmic and coding challenges on CodeWars. Your goal is to accumulate at least 300 points by completing problems across various difficulty levels.

The tasks will improve your problem-solving skills, deepen your understanding of JavaScript (or your chosen language), and enhance your algorithmic thinking.

Objectives

Solve coding challenges on CodeWars to reach 300 points.

Apply knowledge of data structures, algorithms, and problem-solving techniques.

Demonstrate consistent progress by solving challenges across different levels: Kyu 8 → Kyu 1.

Instructions

Go to CodeWars
 and create or log into your account.

Solve coding challenges in the languages you are familiar with.

Track your accumulated points. Your goal is to reach or exceed 300 points.

Copy and paste your CodeWars profile link below to document your checkpoint.

Submission

CodeWars Profile Link: https://www.codewars.com/users/aboje
