Evaluation

Your submission will be evaluated based on:

Total points earned (minimum 300 points)

Variety of challenges solved (preferably across difficulty levels)

Consistency in solving challenges

Notes

Focus on both accuracy and efficiency of your solutions.

Attempt different types of challenges to strengthen problem-solving skills.

Keep a record of completed challenges for future reference.